25
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,536
Hello?

26
00:02:55,536 --> 00:02:57,706
Hania here.

27
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,959
Yes, Hania? What is it?

28
00:02:59,959 --> 00:03:01,856
Do you even bother about Rumi?

29
00:03:01,856 --> 00:03:03,356
Why? What happened?

30
00:03:03,356 --> 00:03:05,650
Did you ever feel that I didn't care about him?

31
00:03:05,650 --> 00:03:06,596
Yes.

32
00:03:06,596 --> 00:03:08,367
