39
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,524
10 minutes from now, yes,

40
00:03:27,524 --> 00:03:28,985
What'd you do tomorrow?

41
00:03:28,985 --> 00:03:30,735
Or the day after?

42
00:03:30,735 --> 00:03:34,786
Obviously, you'd be out of the house if you run a business.

43
00:03:34,786 --> 00:03:37,005
You'd have to leave for work often.

44
00:03:37,005 --> 00:03:39,950
Sometimes, you'd even like to hang out with the lads.

45
00:03:39,950 --> 00:03:43,480
So, please look for a permanent solution, would you?

46
00:03:43,480 --> 00:03:45,080
How?

47
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:47,906
Who's with the kid when he's at home?

48
00:03:47,906 --> 00:03:49,740
