49
00:03:49,740 --> 00:03:53,800
Granted that his Mum's left and is never coming back

50
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:55,869
It's not as if the world has ended!

51
00:03:55,869 --> 00:03:58,480
No, sir, the world is as it was!

52
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:00,390
The same old!

53
00:04:00,390 --> 00:04:02,030
Get married ASAP!

54
00:04:02,030 --> 00:04:03,920
You don't have to worry either,

55
00:04:03,920 --> 00:04:05,980
He's found someone for you, too.

56
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,730
He's friends with her, too.

57
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:10,636
There won't be any issues with a stepmom.

58
00:04:10,636 --> 00:04:12,177
Do you know her?

59
00:04:12,177 --> 00:04:13,536
No.

60
00:04:13,536 --> 00:04:15,818
But he does.

61
00:04:15,818 --> 00:04:19,729
Trust me, he's a rapscallion, but his choice ain't bad.

62
00:04:19,729 --> 00:04:22,620
As in, you haven't the foggiest about who she is.

63
00:04:22,620 --> 00:04:24,110
