70
00:04:37,930 --> 00:04:40,219
She's very cute.

71
00:04:40,219 --> 00:04:42,046
Here's an idea - introduce me to her,

72
00:04:42,046 --> 00:04:44,487
I'll talk to her.

73
00:04:45,177 --> 00:04:47,717
