75
00:04:49,977 --> 00:04:51,387
Should I tell you her name?

76
00:04:51,387 --> 00:04:52,937
Yes?

77
00:04:53,238 --> 00:04:56,179
He's talking about you.

78
00:05:33,380 --> 00:05:35,176
Who are you?

79
00:05:35,176 --> 00:05:38,007
What are you doing at my house?

80
00:05:38,007 --> 00:05:40,060
I think you don't know who I am.

81
00:05:40,060 --> 00:05:42,708
Mr Shehwar, I've got an arrest warrant for you.

82
00:05:42,708 --> 00:05:43,787
What warrant?

83
00:05:43,787 --> 00:05:45,220
What have I done?

84
00:05:45,220 --> 00:05:47,290
Fraud and forgery,

85
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:49,227
Illegal transfer of funds,

86
00:05:49,227 --> 00:05:49,940
And...

87
00:05:49,940 --> 00:05:50,490
And...
-And?

88
00:05:50,490 --> 00:05:54,223
And transferring 1 billion US Dollars through an IOU.

89
00:05:54,223 --> 00:05:55,100
Lies!

90
00:05:55,100 --> 00:05:56,160
Baseless!

91
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:58,226
Prove that in court.

92
00:05:58,226 --> 00:05:59,200
C'mon.

93
00:05:59,200 --> 00:06:00,466
Where?

94
00:06:00,466 --> 00:06:04,300
We're throwing a grand pre-wedding party for you at the lockup. Come,

95
00:06:04,300 --> 00:06:07,260
Or these nice folks here would have to shove you into the car.

96
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:08,487
Who's the complainant?

97
00:06:08,487 --> 00:06:09,848
Your wife,

98
00:06:09,848 --> 00:06:10,910
Maham Syed.

99
00:06:10,910 --> 00:06:12,740
Maham?

100
00:06:13,731 --> 00:06:16,682
Have a good day, dear husband.

101
00:06:20,720 --> 00:06:23,071
Enjoy the party.

102
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,510
Shall we?

103
00:06:25,510 --> 00:06:27,336
I want to talk to my lawyer.

104
00:06:27,336 --> 00:06:28,536
Sure.

105
00:06:28,536 --> 00:06:32,541
I'll get you through as soon as we get there.

106
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:40,346
What are you looking at?

107
00:06:40,346 --> 00:06:42,690
Tell them to stand down.

108
00:06:42,690 --> 00:06:44,626
It's so insulting!

109
00:06:44,626 --> 00:06:48,739
Oh, this is just the beginning...

110
00:06:48,739 --> 00:06:52,730
Just wait and watch what I'll do to you in court!

111
00:06:52,730 --> 00:06:55,159
Now, get lost!

112
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,943
